{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "17.0",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2d290205",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あちゃ～……また実験失敗……やり直しだね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ac9b4042",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最近オーロラは上の空であることが増えた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf7c005a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "実験の失敗の数も増え、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.2",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bf7c005a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今も目の前にモクモクと黒い煙が立ち込めていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "859d18b8",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "ごめんね、今日も実験失敗しちゃって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dbffed68",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、いや、いいんだよ、実験に失敗は付き物だと思うしさ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.2",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "dbffed68",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺が片づけるから、オーロラは休んでて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7fd3d3be",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "うん……ありがとう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b61e76ad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "オーロラが上の空の原因、それは何となくわかっている。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.0",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4f27f30e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "毎日俺を潤んだ瞳で見つめてくるオーロラ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f6f7f8da",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その瞳は何かを求めている、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.2",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f6f7f8da",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ただ何を求めているのかそれがわからなかった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.0",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cd9785a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（もういっそのこと本人に直接聞くのがいいのかな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.2",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cd9785a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "この前のお礼もしたいし、俺にできることは何でもやろう）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.0",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "df4c18ec",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あのさ、オーロラ、何か俺にして欲しいこととかない？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.0",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9724d6c6",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "ん……？　どうしたの突然そんなこと聞いてきて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.0",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a7a252d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、いや……なんとなく、ね……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.2",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a7a252d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "オーロラが俺に何か求めているんじゃないかって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.4",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "a7a252d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もしかして俺の己惚れだったのかな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f709753e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "己惚れなんかじゃないよ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.2",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f709753e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あなたの言っていること、間違っていないから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.0",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "41b4700e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あたしが今一番求めているのはあなた……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.2",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "41b4700e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "ううん、あなたとセックス、したい……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "346993d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "おっオーロラっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a62c630",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "オーロラはそう告げると立ち上がり、衣服を脱ぎだす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb8af3d8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして生まれたままの姿になると、俺の目の前にやってくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2de8fbfa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ白な肌、そして僅かに主張する小さな乳房。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b7f3a9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "無毛なあそこに閉じた割れ目が僅かに見え、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.2",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b7f3a9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その麗しくも可愛らしい裸に、心臓がバクバクと音を立てた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.0",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3c61401e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "ダメ……かな……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.2",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3c61401e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "こんな小さいあたしじゃセックスできないかな……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e0261d3b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あー……いや、その……！　で、できる、と思うけど……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.2",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e0261d3b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ただ、なんで……？　理由教えてくれるかな……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f86e2469",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "最近あなたがほかの娘と話しているのを見ると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.2",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f86e2469",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "なんかこう……胸がもやもやしちゃって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91620e8c",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "嫉妬、しているんだなっていうのは何となくわかるんだけどね……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.2",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "91620e8c",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "重いかな？　こんなこと言われて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.0",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9a3dd1f",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "でも一度だけでいいの……お願いしたいな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.2",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d9a3dd1f",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あなたに抱いて欲しい……あなたと一つになりたいの……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6552ec3e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "普段のふわふわした態度ではなく、真剣な眼差しを向けるオーロラ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "93e7389f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その真摯な態度に断れるはずもなく、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.2",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "93e7389f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺はベルトを外し、ズボンを勢いよく脱ぐ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53a46c8",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "──ひゃっ！？　お、おちんちん……すごいおっきくなってる、ね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.2",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "53a46c8",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "この前見た時よりなんかすごい感じ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "105.0",
      "line_index": 105,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "553f0dc6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もうここまでなったら後戻りできないよ。俺で本当にいい？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "69e4730f",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "うん、あなただからいいの♥　だから抱いて……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.2",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "69e4730f",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あたしをあなたので”女”にして……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "528dbba6",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あうう♥　お尻、熱いぃ……あうっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ef2477c1",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "（ううう……勢いに任せて言っちゃったけど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.2",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ef2477c1",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "いざ本番となると、やっぱり恥ずかしい……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "787fd21c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "オーロラは向き合うのが恥ずかしいのか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.2",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "787fd21c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "身体を隠すようにぎゅっと枕を抱きかかえる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.0",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4f36ac1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな恥じらう姿を見せられ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.2",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b4f36ac1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒がさらにムクムクと勃起してしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cdf2cd72",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "（す、ごい……まだ大きくなってる……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.2",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cdf2cd72",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "それだけあたしで興奮しているのかな……？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.4",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "cdf2cd72",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "それなら嬉しいけど……。でもあんなに大きいの本当に入るの……？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "10294726",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "オーロラは肉棒に目を向けると、不安そうな表情を見せる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d2b01888",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少しでも落ち着かせようと、柔らかな髪を優しく撫でる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.0",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a24d41a6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "優しくするから……もし無理だったら我慢しないで言って",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.0",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eddb8117",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あ、うん……ありがとう……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4330172",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "耳元で優しく囁くと、不安げな表情が消える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.0",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3d1161f0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして同時に僅かに開いている割れ目から、大量の蜜が溢れてきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c1349bf6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それじゃあ……行くよ、オーロラ。身体の力を抜いて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "156.0",
      "line_index": 156,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6971258e",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "うん……来て……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.0",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "12f1ee55",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "はぎゅぅぅ……！　うあ、んぅ……んんんんっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.0",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "302d03ed",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うく……きつい……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "170.0",
      "line_index": 170,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ad47e55d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒の先端を僅かに差し込むも、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "170.2",
      "line_index": 170,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ad47e55d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "小さな膣穴が肉棒を押し戻そうとしてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.0",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6c2f8d65",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "腰にぐっと力を入れると、膣肉をこじ開けるように肉棒を捻じ込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.0",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4e9abd2a",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あ、う……く、う、んぅ……ふ、ふぅぅぅ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cae25e34",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "（大きいの……入って……これ、すごい圧迫感……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.2",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cae25e34",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "息が詰まっちゃう……思っていたより全然大きすぎるぅ……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f852398",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "（でも痛くないし、これなら耐えられる……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.2",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5f852398",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あ、あ……まだ奥に……く、るぅ……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.0",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ed874c",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "あああ……こ、これ……一番奥にぃ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4cfa7a32",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うん、入ったよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.0",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bb0a08e4",
      "speaker": "オーロラ",
      "ja": "ああ、よかった……ちゃんと奥まで入ってくれて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.0",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "35e52bfd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そっとオーロラの頭を撫でると、嬉しそうに微笑む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "194.0",
      "line_index": 194,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d65bbeac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして僅かに力が抜けたのか、肉棒の締め付けが少し緩やかになる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
